title: [No Harassment] Official List of ALL GDers, Assorted By ELO.
body:
https://i.gyazo.com/93de2fc655496d6a43c9e0600ab049c6.png

**ALL HARASSMENT WITHIN THE TIERS HAS BEEN REMOVED MODS. IF YOU DON'T LIKE IT, TELL ME WHATS WRONG BEFORE YOU DELETE IT AND PUNISH. ALOT OF PEOPLE HAD FUN READING IT, AND I PUT QUITE A BIT OF WORK INTO IT. IF ANYONE WANTS THEIR NAME REMOVED, PLEASE SAY SO IN THREAD.**


I will not be assorting by divisions, because this is trivial. Just being in the category of diamond alone gives you full authority and no backtalk should ever be permitted under such circumstances. Platinums also get high authority but they can be backtalked by diamonds. 


This list will take a while to fully compile, so work with me.


*This list does not take into account what someone mains. Any ADC and Support mains should be disregarded instantly; be careful about acknowledging luggage. Furthermore, 100% community-minded & friendly players such as Sweetheart Annie, Tundra Fizz and Besteau will be added at the bottom as they don't try to backtalk and create flawed opinions.
